lead_paragraph: The Massachusetts Gaming Commission on Tuesday awarded a license to build a $1.6 billion casino just outside Boston to Las Vegas developer Wynn Resorts Ltd.

headline.main: Wynn Resorts Wins License to Build Casino Near Boston
